title: UDEMY PFSENSE BEGINNERS TURN ORDINARY PC INTO ENTERPRISE FIREWAL
description:
Hi I m Brian Franklin. I'll show you how I take
ordinary PC and transform it into Enterprise Grade
Firewall

If you need a flexible firewall solution that won t
break the bank, this course is a must

I avoid the tech talk and explain each step in a very down to
earth, easy to understand method. I would dare say you might even
find firewalls delightful after taking this course!

I show you step by step how I install and configure PFsense
firewall software on an ordinary computer

I have personally installed, configured, and deployed over 100
routers and firewalls, including 20+ PfSense
firewalls in real production environments

This course takes you step-by-step through:
PC Preparation
Software Downloading
Installation
Configuration

Not convinced? PfSense competes with and has replaced big name
firewalls such Check Point, Cisco PIX, Cisco ASA, Juniper
Sonicwall, Netgear, Watchguard, Astaro, and others

If you install firewalls or are into firewalls as a hobby, don t
delay

The price will be increasing on: 12/01/2015

Don t Delay, Enroll Today!
